      "content": "the doctors just keep saying \"manage it\" or \"try this new pill\" but they don't get it. they don't live in this body. it's not just \"discomfort,\" it's a constant electric scream. sometimes i just lie there thinking about how much easier it would be if everything just... stopped. like, if there was just silence. wouldn't that be more merciful than this?",
